    <description>As a QBCC Insurance Team Member, I want the following roles added to a unique queue that is able to approve claims of up to $50,000 (Aggregate $60,000) if the postcode associated with them is a regional postcode
Assessment Officer (In the regional Claims permissions set) Senior Assessment Officer (in the regional Claims permissions set)</description>
    <emailTemplate>QBCC_Templates/Claims_Approval_Request</emailTemplate>
    <enableMobileDeviceAccess>false</enableMobileDeviceAccess>
    <entryCriteria>
        <formula>AND(
ISPICKVAL(Claim_Approval_Status__c, &quot;Pre-Approval&quot;),
NOT ISBLANK(Schedule__r.Quote__c),
Total_Claim_Approval_Amount__c &lt;= 50000,
Aggregate_and_Claim_Pending_Amount__c &lt;= 60000,
NOT ISPICKVAL(Schedule__r.Related_Case__r.CaseAssessmentRegion__c, &quot;Brisbane&quot;)
)</formula>
    </entryCriteria>
